headline: Carrier Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Advisory
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, will release its third quarter 2025 earnings on Tuesday, October 28, 2025 and host a conference call and webcast at 7:30 a.m. ET.

headline: Carrier Global’s Q3 2025 Earnings: What to Expect
summary: Carrier Global is scheduled to announce its third-quarter results later this month, with analysts expecting a double-digit decline in profits.
